WEBVTT

01:36.900 --> 01:41.009
[The Best Thing]

01:41.360 --> 01:48.500
Episode 16: Cinnabar
Taste: Sweet
Nature: Slightly cold, toxic
Meridian Entry: Heart
Functions: Clears the heart, calms fright, also detoxifies

01:55.509 --> 01:56.680
Did you gain weight during the New Year?

01:56.680 --> 01:57.350
Happy New Year.

01:57.350 --> 01:58.430
Happy New Year.

01:58.430 --> 01:59.560
Mr. Lin, you're a bit early.

01:59.560 --> 02:00.760
Happy New Year.

02:00.760 --> 02:01.840
I gained 7.3 jin.

02:01.840 --> 02:03.400
You're so precise.

02:08.220 --> 02:08.850
Thank you.

02:09.410 --> 02:10.130
Have some candy, have some candy.

02:10.160 --> 02:10.600
Happy New Year.

02:10.630 --> 02:11.750
Have some candy, come have some candy.

03:08.360 --> 03:09.560
You're in your thirties.

03:09.560 --> 03:11.680
Drinking so much bubble tea, you'll get fat.

03:11.680 --> 03:13.210
It's none of your business if I get fat or not.

03:14.000 --> 03:15.310
What's going on between you two?

03:15.310 --> 03:17.079
What are you arguing about?

03:17.079 --> 03:19.190
It's nothing. I don't want to talk to him.

03:19.190 --> 03:20.470
I don't want to talk to you either.

03:20.470 --> 03:21.400
Come on, drink some bubble tea.

03:22.450 --> 03:23.240
Stop drinking.

03:23.310 --> 03:24.560
Why can't I drink? I'll drink if I want to.

03:24.560 --> 03:25.680
Just let him drink.

03:25.680 --> 03:26.590
It's my treat this time.

03:26.590 --> 03:27.430
Let him drink.

03:27.800 --> 03:29.360
Fine, you drink. I'm leaving.

03:29.360 --> 03:30.030
Wait a moment.

03:30.740 --> 03:33.340
This is a gift specially from my parents for you.

03:33.370 --> 03:34.000
Just take it.

03:34.030 --> 03:35.000
Don't be angry anymore.

03:40.230 --> 03:41.320
Is this for me?

03:41.400 --> 03:42.360
Yes, it's yours.

03:42.829 --> 03:45.510
You, go after her. Stop drinking.

03:46.070 --> 03:47.230
Oh, stop drinking.

03:49.150 --> 03:50.079
Xu Xiangya.

03:51.000 --> 03:51.590
Wait a moment.

03:51.590 --> 03:52.300
Let me talk to you.

03:58.630 --> 03:59.630
Xifan.

03:59.920 --> 04:00.630
Do you know

04:00.630 --> 04:03.080
what's going on with Xiangya and Mr. Lin today?

04:03.590 --> 04:04.900
They're at odds with each other.

04:05.690 --> 04:06.630
Leave them alone.

04:07.090 --> 04:08.450
They're always like this.

04:09.280 --> 04:10.120
That's true.

04:18.040 --> 04:18.750
What's wrong?

04:19.440 --> 04:20.430
The bus is here.

04:20.459 --> 04:21.339
What's the matter?

04:21.490 --> 04:22.660
Good news.

04:22.810 --> 04:24.360
Good news? What's going on?

04:24.390 --> 04:25.160
Tell me about it.

04:26.560 --> 04:28.040
The weather is so nice today, look.

04:47.159 --> 04:48.000
Alright then.

04:48.880 --> 04:51.050
You'll still graduate with your master's degree under my supervision.

04:51.950 --> 04:54.270
After advancing to your doctoral studies, you can transfer to the gynecology department.

04:54.750 --> 04:55.600
This afternoon,

04:55.600 --> 04:57.480
I'll contact Director Zhao from the gynecology department.

04:57.830 --> 04:59.270
I'll ask him to be your doctoral supervisor.

04:59.630 --> 05:00.560
Thank you, Professor.

05:03.120 --> 05:04.000
That's quite good.

05:05.070 --> 05:08.160
It's a good thing to find your own ideas and goals before

05:08.720 --> 05:09.870
starting your doctoral studies.

05:12.640 --> 05:13.870
If there's nothing else,

05:14.160 --> 05:15.430
I’ll leave now.

05:15.430 --> 05:17.920
I have a meeting at the Third Hospital this afternoon.

05:18.240 --> 05:18.560
Okay.

05:18.560 --> 05:19.520
Then I'll see you out.

05:19.750 --> 05:20.390
No need.

05:20.890 --> 05:22.450
You should prepare for your rounds.

05:23.720 --> 05:24.560
I'll be going then.

05:24.560 --> 05:25.470
Goodbye, Professor.

05:25.600 --> 05:26.160
Goodbye.

05:37.190 --> 05:38.040
Senior He.

05:43.630 --> 05:44.480
Have you made up your mind?

05:45.280 --> 05:46.480
You're transferring to the gynecology department?

05:49.720 --> 05:50.830
I've been thinking about it for a while.

05:52.240 --> 05:53.560
I think what you said makes sense.

05:54.000 --> 05:55.270
I don't want to

05:55.270 --> 05:57.630
have my achievements and efforts discredited one day.

05:59.159 --> 06:01.560
Although this might not necessarily happen,

06:01.830 --> 06:03.710
I need to consider my own interests.

06:04.630 --> 06:05.510
Moreover,

06:05.790 --> 06:09.440
I feel that oncology doesn't really suit me.

06:09.950 --> 06:11.390
The atmosphere is too depressing.

06:12.310 --> 06:13.360
So,

06:13.760 --> 06:16.000
I'll take this opportunity to transfer to gynecology.

06:16.620 --> 06:18.010
During my doctoral studies,

06:18.040 --> 06:20.040
I want to research women's health issues.

06:22.630 --> 06:24.000
This direction suits you well.

06:25.630 --> 06:26.360
I think so too.

06:27.970 --> 06:30.000
Alright, hurry back to school.

06:30.750 --> 06:31.870
Get some rest while you can.

06:32.030 --> 06:33.760
The internship in gynecology will be even more demanding.

06:49.580 --> 06:50.780
Good luck, Senior He.

06:51.610 --> 06:53.409
Thank you for mentoring me during my internship these past two years.

06:58.580 --> 06:59.850
It's part of my job.

07:53.510 --> 07:55.040
What's the deal with this picture?

07:55.070 --> 07:56.950
You two, explain this to me right now.

07:56.970 --> 07:58.060
Confess immediately.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.120
Mom, what's wrong?

08:08.530 --> 08:09.650
I'll land after 10 p.m.

08:09.680 --> 08:11.230
It'll be midnight by the time I get home.

08:13.950 --> 08:15.310
Why such a rush?

08:15.960 --> 08:17.400
Let's talk about it after the New Year.

08:18.070 --> 08:19.270
Don't we have to do a thorough cleaning tomorrow

08:19.270 --> 08:21.070
and prepare for the New Year's Eve dinner and such?

08:22.600 --> 08:24.160
Alright, alright, I'm at the airport now.

08:24.160 --> 08:25.430
I've got to go now.

08:25.430 --> 08:26.040
Bye-bye.

08:28.050 --> 08:29.400
Shs's calling you back for a blind date, huh?

08:34.120 --> 08:35.480
Why pretend to be so reluctant?

08:35.850 --> 08:37.760
Wasn't it already arranged for you to go back for a blind date?

08:38.870 --> 08:40.080
I hope your blind date is successful.

08:46.320 --> 08:47.080
What?

09:00.120 --> 09:01.600
We've known each other for almost ten years, right?

09:02.690 --> 09:04.330
You should know what kind of person I am by now.

09:04.590 --> 09:05.550
I like you.

09:07.130 --> 09:08.040
Do you want to be together with me?

09:10.710 --> 09:12.240
We can't be just friends anymore anyway.

09:13.240 --> 09:14.630
Even if we break up in the future,

09:15.030 --> 09:16.030
the worst outcome would just be

09:16.030 --> 09:17.030
not being able to be friends, right?

09:17.360 --> 09:18.840
I'll quit and go back to my hometown then.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.200
I won't be in your way at all.

09:23.750 --> 09:25.000
So, what do you say?

09:46.580 --> 09:48.150
Is this result okay?

10:17.700 --> 10:20.390
Oh, so it started before the New Year?

10:20.410 --> 10:22.010
And no one told me?

10:23.120 --> 10:25.270
I thought you two were really angry with each other.

10:25.750 --> 10:28.080
We didn't want other colleagues to know.

10:28.390 --> 10:30.030
After all, we work in the same place.

10:31.550 --> 10:33.000
We didn't say anything during the New Year

10:33.000 --> 10:34.840
because it was a bit awkward.

10:35.380 --> 10:37.020
We were looking for a chance to tell you.

10:37.510 --> 10:39.600
We were planning to tell you

10:39.600 --> 10:40.390
after the morning meeting.

10:40.390 --> 10:41.630
But the way you were teased by us

10:41.630 --> 10:42.720
was really funny.

10:45.670 --> 10:46.480
Fine.

10:46.480 --> 10:47.910
So you two teamed up to play me, huh?

10:48.550 --> 10:49.390
By the way,

10:50.160 --> 10:51.400
your acting is really bad.

10:52.030 --> 10:53.600
It could only fool her.

10:54.390 --> 10:56.790
Alright, alright, my acting is bad.

10:56.790 --> 10:57.870
Your acting is good.

10:58.320 --> 10:59.480
The day she gave the gift,

10:59.510 --> 11:00.750
you didn't even finish your lines

11:00.770 --> 11:01.470
before you walked away,

11:01.490 --> 11:02.770
leaving me here alone.

11:03.760 --> 11:04.630
Enough.

11:05.680 --> 11:06.710
So, are you two

11:06.730 --> 11:08.370
planning to keep this a secret forever?

11:08.570 --> 11:09.380
No, we won't.

11:10.580 --> 11:12.420
I'm planning to quit with you when the time comes.

11:16.060 --> 11:17.730
I've been thinking about it for a long time.

11:18.270 --> 11:20.080
Working in hotel food service,

11:20.600 --> 11:21.870
besides our main duties,

11:22.090 --> 11:24.260
there are too many things to worry about.

11:25.030 --> 11:26.550
When researching new dishes,

11:26.570 --> 11:27.880
I feel particularly limited.

11:28.270 --> 11:28.840
So,

11:29.200 --> 11:31.270
I might as well quit with you

11:31.270 --> 11:32.110
and find a new environment.

11:32.710 --> 11:35.830
It also avoids office romance, right?

11:37.550 --> 11:38.670
Then I'll stay here.

11:38.960 --> 11:39.960
After you graduate and come back,

11:39.960 --> 11:41.550
if you want to come back to work,

11:42.080 --> 11:43.750
we can still be colleagues.

11:48.240 --> 11:48.910
Okay.

11:49.750 --> 11:50.440
Are you not angry anymore?

11:51.540 --> 11:52.330
Not anymore.

11:52.950 --> 11:54.480
That's good.

11:54.600 --> 11:55.840
What's going on with you two?

11:55.840 --> 11:57.320
Let go of each other's hand. What are you doing?

11:58.240 --> 11:59.240
But seriously though,

11:59.790 --> 12:01.120
I've come to realize

12:01.120 --> 12:03.630
that when two people have feelings for each other but insist on being just friends,

12:04.620 --> 12:06.310
it's bound to come to an end.

12:07.240 --> 12:08.550
So why not just start dating?

12:09.150 --> 12:10.510
The worst outcome is breaking up,

12:10.510 --> 12:11.550
and not even being able to be friends.

12:12.300 --> 12:13.630
At least there won't be any regrets.

12:17.640 --> 12:19.280
So, you and Dr. He...

12:19.300 --> 12:20.090
Stop.

12:21.050 --> 12:23.140
Why are you suddenly talking about me?

12:31.030 --> 12:32.650
[Oncology]

12:34.440 --> 12:35.750
Where's today's homework?

12:39.190 --> 12:42.100
You seem to look forward to my dad's daily assignments, huh?

12:51.500 --> 12:53.720
My dad is in charge of cooking at home,

12:53.970 --> 12:55.490
but he didn't cook today,

12:55.510 --> 12:56.870
so there's no homework.

13:05.240 --> 13:05.920
Okay.

13:26.640 --> 13:29.070
I'm still looking forward to seeing you.

13:31.510 --> 13:33.160
Dr. He, a patient has arrived.

13:33.300 --> 13:33.970
Come in.

13:34.510 --> 13:35.270
-Let’s go for dinner.
-Let’s go.

13:47.790 --> 13:48.790
Xifan, let's go.

13:51.410 --> 13:53.440
Maybe I should go back first.

13:53.470 --> 13:54.470
Where are you going back to?

13:54.510 --> 13:55.080
Your parents

13:55.080 --> 13:56.120
went hiking today, didn't they?

13:56.120 --> 13:57.440
You won't have anything to eat if you go home.

13:58.950 --> 13:59.680
That's right.

14:05.490 --> 14:06.010
Well,

14:06.960 --> 14:07.550
let's go.

14:11.030 --> 14:12.630
Everything else is fine.

14:13.240 --> 14:14.390
Just remember,

14:14.720 --> 14:16.030
don't drink alcohol after taking the medication.

14:19.510 --> 14:19.870
Okay.

14:19.870 --> 14:20.510
Thank you, Dr. He.

14:20.510 --> 14:20.870
You're welcome.

14:20.870 --> 14:21.630
It's my duty.

15:04.630 --> 15:07.870
Please be careful as the vehicle enters the station.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.360
Okay, okay, alright.

15:27.360 --> 15:28.910
Okay, please have a seat.

15:28.910 --> 15:29.480
It'll be ready in a moment.

15:51.250 --> 15:52.320
Oh my!

16:10.250 --> 16:11.050
He Suye.

16:22.150 --> 16:23.600
Why are you so late?

16:24.150 --> 16:24.840
Sit down.

16:26.420 --> 16:27.940
I just saw your WeChat message.

16:28.530 --> 16:29.320
You're lying.

16:30.770 --> 16:32.650
I bought so much alcohol for you.

16:34.110 --> 16:35.660
I wanted to drink it with you.

16:36.340 --> 16:37.690
And you only show up now.

16:41.020 --> 16:41.900
You've had too much to drink.

16:57.180 --> 16:57.870
You fickle woman.

17:01.270 --> 17:02.220
Me?

17:06.869 --> 17:07.790
Why?

17:10.349 --> 17:12.349
You are fickle.

17:19.960 --> 17:20.640
Fine.

17:22.400 --> 17:24.920
Then tell me how I'm fickle.

17:28.530 --> 17:31.160
You were the one who hooked me first.

17:32.260 --> 17:34.870
You caught me and then let me go.

17:35.200 --> 17:35.880
I...

17:36.340 --> 17:38.100
I clearly sent you red beans.

17:38.130 --> 17:38.940
Did you eat them?

17:39.300 --> 17:40.580
Did you come for your follow-up visit?

17:43.430 --> 17:44.600
What kind of person does that?

17:44.920 --> 17:47.080
What kind of fish,

17:47.110 --> 17:50.190
spits red beans back at the person who caught it?

17:52.130 --> 17:53.440
Look at me.

17:54.030 --> 17:54.790
Just like this.

18:02.030 --> 18:03.550
Today, I...

18:03.550 --> 18:06.240
went to dinner with Senior Lin and the others.

18:06.640 --> 18:09.470
so I haven't had a chance to eat the red beans yet,

18:09.640 --> 18:11.430
and I haven't had time for the follow-up visit either.

18:12.120 --> 18:12.990
Besides,

18:13.880 --> 18:14.990
how did I hook you?

18:15.110 --> 18:16.200
You did.

18:16.990 --> 18:17.840
No, I didn't.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.680
You hooked me right there.

18:26.800 --> 18:30.120
He Suye, thank you for liking me.

18:34.920 --> 18:36.570
You’re drunk. I’ll take you back.

18:36.600 --> 18:37.430
I'm not leaving.

18:38.360 --> 18:39.400
-Let’s go.
-No.

18:43.240 --> 18:44.150
He Suye.

18:44.780 --> 18:46.870
I remember someone told me,

18:47.240 --> 18:50.310
drinking and then being in the wind in this weather can cause a cold.

18:50.630 --> 18:53.550
What, were you lying to me before?

19:19.290 --> 19:20.680
Take me home, please.

19:25.890 --> 19:27.850
Since you hooked me first,

19:28.670 --> 19:30.120
you'll have to be responsible for me.

19:30.960 --> 19:32.240
You can't just abandon me.

19:34.030 --> 19:34.960
Alright.

19:36.260 --> 19:37.590
I won't abandon you.

19:38.210 --> 19:39.350
I'll take you home.

19:39.530 --> 19:40.920
Come on, lift your arms.

19:43.740 --> 19:45.510
You're so heavy.

19:45.640 --> 19:47.750
How can you be such a lightweight and still love to drink?

19:47.790 --> 19:48.850
It's the opposite way.

19:48.940 --> 19:49.700
This way goes to my house.

19:51.110 --> 19:52.580
And garbage all over the place.

19:53.120 --> 19:54.680
I'll come back to clean it up later.

19:55.550 --> 19:56.510
He Suye.

19:58.310 --> 19:59.550
Put me down, put me down.

19:59.770 --> 20:00.580
Password, password.

20:00.610 --> 20:01.130
Enter the password.

20:02.350 --> 20:04.390
You, don't look.

20:10.070 --> 20:11.500
Can you wash up by yourself?

20:12.590 --> 20:12.920
Then I...

20:12.920 --> 20:13.510
No problem.

20:13.510 --> 20:14.070
I'm leaving, okay?

20:14.870 --> 20:15.990
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

20:22.680 --> 20:23.660
Xifan.

20:27.440 --> 20:28.160
Good night.

20:31.030 --> 20:31.640
Good night.

20:38.030 --> 20:38.640
Fickle woman.

20:51.430 --> 20:53.220
You were the one who hooked me first.

20:53.790 --> 20:55.310
How come you caught me

20:55.710 --> 20:56.970
and then let me go?

21:05.250 --> 21:07.210
I don't think this counts as hooking him.

21:25.080 --> 21:25.910
Dinner's ready.

21:26.550 --> 21:27.270
Coming.

21:28.700 --> 21:29.540
Where are the soup bowls?

21:30.550 --> 21:31.480
I forgot them.

21:31.960 --> 21:32.510
I'll get them.

21:34.700 --> 21:36.630
Mr. Shen has created a new dish again.

21:37.160 --> 21:38.750
The last dish in the medicated diet menu.

21:38.970 --> 21:40.410
Red bean and crucian carp soup.

21:40.510 --> 21:41.170
Alright.

21:43.120 --> 21:43.790
Serve the soup.

21:43.810 --> 21:44.570
Oh, okay.

21:46.930 --> 21:48.370
What kind of person does that?

21:48.400 --> 21:50.680
What kind of fish,

21:50.700 --> 21:53.660
spits red beans back at the person who caught it?

21:53.900 --> 21:54.660
Look at me.

21:55.030 --> 21:55.750
Just like this.

21:58.510 --> 22:01.030
You need to flip this fish over.

22:01.570 --> 22:02.850
Only if you flip it over

22:02.880 --> 22:05.810
can you see the red beans in the soup, you know?

22:05.840 --> 22:06.840
Like this.

22:12.080 --> 22:13.360
You've scattered it.

22:13.380 --> 22:14.450
Hey, hurry and serve the soup.

22:17.230 --> 22:18.070
The first bowl

22:18.960 --> 22:20.200
goes to Ms. Shen first.

22:22.720 --> 22:24.040
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

22:25.140 --> 22:26.380
Ms. Liu.

22:26.410 --> 22:28.280
Your soup looks kind of scary.

22:28.300 --> 22:29.300
Can it taste good?

22:29.350 --> 22:30.310
This soup

22:30.790 --> 22:31.720
nourishes the spleen and boosts energy.

22:31.840 --> 22:32.990
It's especially good for women.

22:33.070 --> 22:34.400
It tastes really good.

22:36.040 --> 22:36.680
It's alright.

22:36.710 --> 22:37.880
It even cures constipation.

22:38.560 --> 22:39.710
Then you'd better drink more.

22:43.120 --> 22:46.280
♫A light scent♫

22:49.180 --> 22:53.430
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

22:55.400 --> 22:59.570
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

23:00.480 --> 23:07.070
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

23:03.310 --> 23:04.240
Homework.

23:08.380 --> 23:11.260
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

23:14.260 --> 23:18.860
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

23:20.690 --> 23:25.040
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

23:25.400 --> 23:26.400
Red bean.

23:25.550 --> 23:30.950
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

23:26.720 --> 23:27.640
Fish soup.

23:29.390 --> 23:30.350
You did it on purpose.

23:33.430 --> 23:36.890
♫Longing adjusts its frequency♫

23:39.520 --> 23:44.250
♫Resonating with our expectations♫

23:45.770 --> 23:49.870
♫The little challenges that time has given us♫

23:50.740 --> 23:56.020
♫Are meant to deepen the meaning of loving you♫

24:00.920 --> 24:01.510
Roger.

24:01.020 --> 24:06.290
♫Using my breath♫

24:07.300 --> 24:13.340
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

24:13.540 --> 24:16.350
♫To merge in♫

24:19.470 --> 24:22.860
♫The air♫

24:26.220 --> 24:30.760
♫Love becomes familiar♫

24:30.880 --> 24:35.380
♫Using my breath♫

24:33.590 --> 24:36.030
How old are you to still act cute?

24:35.660 --> 24:41.880
♫Breathe the fragrance of your heart♫

24:36.030 --> 24:37.110
Aren't you embarrassed?

24:39.070 --> 24:40.110
You don't understand.

24:41.900 --> 24:44.530
♫Love is♫

24:42.680 --> 24:43.550
You'd better be careful.

24:43.550 --> 24:44.880
Don't throw out your back.

24:47.660 --> 24:51.440
♫The air♫

24:54.500 --> 24:57.960
♫It's you♫

24:59.230 --> 25:01.230
♫Who always follow you♫

25:02.960 --> 25:05.270
The guest list of March is out.

25:05.270 --> 25:06.350
Many of them are returning customers.

25:06.350 --> 25:08.070
Please prepare in advance, everyone.

25:08.450 --> 25:10.930
The team from Zhongyu Technology will also be checking in this week.

25:11.160 --> 25:12.750
Zhongyu Technology attended the IT summit

25:12.750 --> 25:13.960
here last year.

25:14.200 --> 25:15.270
In the list is a director

25:15.270 --> 25:17.160
called Yan Heng.

25:20.130 --> 25:22.370
He's the younger son of CEO Yan from Zhongyu Technology.

25:23.290 --> 25:25.570
He started a small robotics company abroad.

25:26.790 --> 25:27.720
He's won quite a few awards.

25:28.880 --> 25:31.110
He's a rising star in the industry.

25:32.130 --> 25:33.960
We must provide excellent service to Young Mr. Yan

25:33.990 --> 25:34.960
as well as his team this time.

25:35.900 --> 25:37.170
We need to secure this client.

26:46.240 --> 26:47.400
Hello, Young Mr. Yan.

27:01.030 --> 27:01.830
Hello, sir.

27:01.830 --> 27:03.400
Here are your ID and room key.

27:03.400 --> 27:03.640
Thank you.

27:03.640 --> 27:05.030
Please sign here, thank you.

27:29.140 --> 27:29.970
Young Mr. Yan,

27:30.270 --> 27:32.120
your villa is ready for you.

27:32.150 --> 27:33.190
Our Marketing Department manager...

27:33.210 --> 27:33.910
Long time no see.

27:34.110 --> 27:35.240
Long time no see, Young Mr. Yan.

27:35.430 --> 27:36.600
You... you know each other?

27:36.880 --> 27:37.790
We're old friends.

27:38.750 --> 27:39.430
This way, please.

27:39.770 --> 27:40.160
Okay.

27:41.990 --> 27:42.600
They know each other?

27:44.310 --> 27:45.480
He should have said so earlier.

27:45.930 --> 27:46.690
Manager,

27:47.550 --> 27:48.790
Mr. Yan particularly dislikes

27:48.790 --> 27:49.830
being called "Young Mr. Yan."

27:50.120 --> 27:51.400
Please be mindful of this in the future.

27:54.230 --> 27:55.360
I'm terribly sorry.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.750
I'll inform our colleagues right away.

27:56.750 --> 27:57.260
Alright?

27:57.370 --> 27:58.210
I apologize.

27:58.350 --> 27:59.640
Could you please...

28:01.070 --> 28:01.680
Tell us about it.

28:24.400 --> 28:26.550
Mr. Yan, this is the housekeeping supervisor

28:26.550 --> 28:28.350
and the housekeeper who will be in charge of all your accommodation matters

28:28.350 --> 28:29.160
during your stay.

28:29.160 --> 28:30.790
-Tell him if you need anything...
-Where’s Xifan?

28:32.470 --> 28:34.310
Manager Shen is in charge of housekeeping for the entire hotel.

28:34.310 --> 28:35.310
She apologizes for any inconvenience.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.480
If you have any needs or issues,

28:36.480 --> 28:37.680
you can ask them to help you resolve them.

28:44.950 --> 28:45.920
Help with the luggage.

28:54.930 --> 28:56.630
[Yuncong All Day Dining Restaurant]

29:48.500 --> 29:50.260
Don't mind him, go about your business.

30:04.950 --> 30:06.230
I'll be back in the country after Spring Festival.

30:06.790 --> 30:08.030
Let's have a meal together.

30:08.540 --> 30:09.250
I've missed you.

30:47.830 --> 30:48.680
Long time no see.

30:49.440 --> 30:50.680
It's not dinner time yet.

30:50.680 --> 30:52.030
Would you like a drink first?

30:52.720 --> 30:53.330
Thank you.

30:54.070 --> 30:55.270
Tropical fruit juice.

30:55.270 --> 30:56.720
Made with all imported fruits.

30:57.000 --> 30:58.350
To let you experience

30:58.350 --> 31:00.440
a different Southeast Asian flavor in winter, Mr. Yan.

31:01.250 --> 31:01.940
Sorry.

31:02.020 --> 31:03.130
I'm allergic to mangoes.

31:03.160 --> 31:04.690
Could you please help me change this drink?

31:04.960 --> 31:06.050
I'm sorry.

31:06.080 --> 31:07.920
I wasn't aware of this situation beforehand.

31:11.670 --> 31:13.190
I'm here to see Xifan.

31:13.210 --> 31:14.260
Do you know where she is?

31:14.790 --> 31:15.680
She's probably at work.

31:17.190 --> 31:19.400
Could you please help me contact her?

31:21.180 --> 31:22.780
Can't you reach her?

31:25.440 --> 31:26.150
I remember it now.

31:26.590 --> 31:28.440
It seems like she's blocked you, hasn't she?

31:30.230 --> 31:33.120
Why don't you look around, Mr. Yan?

31:33.140 --> 31:34.730
Our hotel is quite large indeed.

31:34.760 --> 31:36.330
But she must be somewhere around here.

31:41.540 --> 31:42.340
You all

31:43.410 --> 31:44.610
are helping her hide from me, aren't you?

31:45.490 --> 31:47.050
It seems like you're the one who's been hiding, doesn't it?

31:47.520 --> 31:49.760
You didn't even show your face when you broke up with her.

31:49.880 --> 31:51.160
And now you suddenly appear.

31:51.380 --> 31:52.460
What do you mean?

31:55.960 --> 31:56.930
I want to get back together with her.

32:00.060 --> 32:02.250
What makes you think she wants to get back together with you?

32:02.830 --> 32:05.460
She's doing very well and is happy now.

32:05.480 --> 32:06.310
What makes you think

32:06.310 --> 32:07.790
she would take you back?

32:12.400 --> 32:13.110
What do you mean?

32:17.240 --> 32:18.570
Does she have a new boyfriend now?

32:18.600 --> 32:19.600
It's none of your business.

32:35.720 --> 32:38.000
Where did this Southeast Asian-style set meal come from?

32:38.220 --> 32:39.550
You're the Food & Beverage manager.

32:39.640 --> 32:40.550
How could you take the lead in violating

32:40.550 --> 32:41.880
the most basic service standards?

32:42.190 --> 32:44.120
You actually threatened customers with food safety.

32:44.950 --> 32:46.670
I'm sorry, General Manager.

32:46.750 --> 32:47.920
Please deduct my bonus.

32:47.940 --> 32:48.900
Of course I will deduct it.

32:50.200 --> 32:51.480
There will also be a public criticism tomorrow.

32:53.680 --> 32:55.400
I'm sorry, General Manager.

32:56.310 --> 32:57.960
Alright, alright. Get back to work now.

32:59.050 --> 33:00.090
Go, go, go!

33:12.900 --> 33:16.090
[Manager of Front Office]

33:50.310 --> 33:51.200
What's going on here?

33:52.110 --> 33:53.700
Come on, please solve this!

33:54.710 --> 33:55.800
You go!

33:56.330 --> 33:58.080
Am I the general manager? Go.

33:58.790 --> 34:00.160
You go first!

34:00.350 --> 34:01.350
Hurry up, hurry up, hurry up!

34:07.510 --> 34:09.360
Mr. Yan. Well...

34:09.360 --> 34:12.070
Why don't you go back to the villa and rest for a while?

34:12.070 --> 34:13.150
I'll definitely...

34:23.949 --> 34:28.070
Where are you? Come to the lobby right now, immediately!

34:32.280 --> 34:33.150
What should we do about this?

34:34.570 --> 34:35.699
Go back to the office and take a break.

34:36.320 --> 34:37.440
Go, go, go!

34:37.989 --> 34:38.719
Then I'll head back first.

35:03.440 --> 35:03.960
Shen.

35:03.960 --> 35:04.510
Auntie.

35:04.510 --> 35:05.000
Busy?

35:05.000 --> 35:06.150
I have something to do.

35:18.480 --> 35:19.110
Xifan.

35:19.850 --> 35:20.640
Mr. Yan,

35:21.730 --> 35:22.370
This is for you.

35:30.920 --> 35:31.670
You've worked hard.

35:40.880 --> 35:42.590
Manager Shen's boyfriend?

35:44.710 --> 35:46.000
So rich!

35:49.810 --> 35:50.690
What time do you get off work?

35:51.900 --> 35:52.650
Five o'clock.

35:52.770 --> 35:53.400
Let me give you a ride.

35:53.420 --> 35:54.020
No need.

35:54.890 --> 35:56.490
I can take the company bus.

35:57.550 --> 35:58.030
It's no trouble.

35:58.030 --> 35:58.620
Mr. Yan.

36:04.130 --> 36:05.670
Do you have anything else?

36:06.150 --> 36:07.420
Let's talk somewhere else.

36:10.330 --> 36:10.950
Okay.

36:14.920 --> 36:15.730
Please.

36:38.780 --> 36:40.020
I remember.

36:40.370 --> 36:41.000
That Mr. Yan

36:41.000 --> 36:42.630
is Manager Shen's boyfriend, right?

36:44.550 --> 36:45.800
They broke up long ago.

36:46.110 --> 36:46.800
If others spread rumors,

36:46.830 --> 36:48.060
please help clarify it.

37:11.150 --> 37:12.280
Why don't we go to my room?

37:12.300 --> 37:13.380
We can sit and talk.

37:22.470 --> 37:23.400
Shen Xifan.

37:23.520 --> 37:25.290
Being your boyfriend is too tiring.

37:25.580 --> 37:26.870
You don't care about me at all.

37:27.110 --> 37:28.510
You only care about yourself.

37:29.080 --> 37:30.370
You're too selfish.

37:31.250 --> 37:32.520
I just love you too much.

37:33.030 --> 37:35.150
That's why I didn't realize you've always been this selfish.

37:36.410 --> 37:37.080
Xifan,

37:37.370 --> 37:38.520
I've been thinking for a long time.

37:38.840 --> 37:39.950
We should break up.

38:11.530 --> 38:12.170
Xifan,

38:16.070 --> 38:17.240
let's get back together.

38:20.280 --> 38:21.150
Get back together?

38:21.670 --> 38:23.510
I was really too busy last year.

38:23.550 --> 38:24.920
The company's self-developed robot

38:24.920 --> 38:25.760
needed to apply for patents,

38:25.760 --> 38:26.760
go public, and compete for awards.

38:27.000 --> 38:28.110
I also had to deal with Zhongyu's acquisition

38:28.110 --> 38:28.990
and handle my father.

38:29.010 --> 38:30.970
During that time, I was really stretched thin, I didn't...

38:33.760 --> 38:35.150
After I finished all that and came to my senses,

38:35.150 --> 38:36.110
I really regretted it.

38:36.520 --> 38:37.960
I shouldn't have lost my temper at you.

38:38.510 --> 38:39.510
I shouldn't have argued with you.

38:39.510 --> 38:40.800
We didn't just argue.

38:40.800 --> 38:42.000
We broke up, okay?

38:42.140 --> 38:43.460
Our seven years of love,

38:43.900 --> 38:45.380
how could we just break up like this?

38:48.190 --> 38:48.960
Xifan, listen to me.

38:48.960 --> 38:49.920
Don't touch me.

38:51.650 --> 38:52.480
Go away.

39:10.740 --> 39:11.740
It's okay.

39:12.200 --> 39:13.200
We're all here.

39:18.340 --> 39:19.490
What did he tell you?

39:23.050 --> 39:24.970
He's not trying to get back together with you, is he?

39:39.270 --> 39:40.980
He came to see me today.

39:43.000 --> 39:43.800
He said

39:46.230 --> 39:48.070
he was too busy with work before,

39:48.070 --> 39:49.440
so he neglected me.

39:51.670 --> 39:53.830
He said he really regrets it now.

39:58.990 --> 39:59.990
Tell me,

40:01.070 --> 40:02.510
what am I

40:03.340 --> 40:04.740
to him after all?

40:10.720 --> 40:13.400
I actually thought of so many things before,

40:13.430 --> 40:14.710
things I wanted to say to scold him.

40:15.940 --> 40:17.620
I thought about it day and night.

40:20.710 --> 40:21.880
but when he stood in front of me,

40:21.880 --> 40:23.630
I couldn't remember a single word.

40:28.330 --> 40:30.520
Why couldn't I remember anything?

40:45.210 --> 40:46.520
It's okay, it's okay.

40:52.480 --> 40:56.160
[Gunan Huating Manor]

41:02.960 --> 41:05.250
I heard your supervisor is Mr. Yan's ex-girlfriend.

41:05.700 --> 41:07.050
Stop it.

41:14.620 --> 41:15.510
Have you heard

41:15.510 --> 41:17.480
between Manager Shen and the customer?

41:17.480 --> 41:18.440
What is it?

41:18.440 --> 41:19.590
Let me tell you,

41:19.590 --> 41:21.320
it's about that Mr. Yan, Yan Heng.

41:21.850 --> 41:23.030
You mean him?

41:23.030 --> 41:23.670
If I were her,

41:23.670 --> 41:24.440
I'd marry into a rich family

41:24.440 --> 41:26.070
and become a wealthy wife instead of coming to work.

41:26.070 --> 41:27.590
Yeah. That Mr. Yan

41:27.590 --> 41:28.920
is handsome and rich.

41:28.920 --> 41:30.000
What is she doing?

41:30.000 --> 41:31.440
You don't understand.

41:31.440 --> 41:33.030
The more difficult a woman is, the more men love her.

41:41.800 --> 41:43.400
Manager Shen, due to personal reasons,

41:42.560 --> 41:44.400
[Meeting Hall]

41:43.450 --> 41:44.770
has become entangled with a customer,

41:45.060 --> 41:46.740
which has affected the hotel's operations,

41:46.920 --> 41:47.950
called our service into question,

41:48.320 --> 41:49.630
and damaged our reputation.

41:50.210 --> 41:51.410
We must criticize this behavior.

41:51.720 --> 41:52.990
This month's bonus of hers will be deducted.

41:53.770 --> 41:56.000
All department managers should use this as a negative example

41:56.020 --> 41:57.660
to educate and warn their staff.

41:57.880 --> 41:59.200
When working in a hotel,

41:59.220 --> 42:00.780
one should maintain a professional attitude

42:00.810 --> 42:02.160
and keep a distance from customers.

42:02.280 --> 42:04.200
Wasn't this covered in our orientation training?

42:06.520 --> 42:07.400
Manager Shen,

42:07.960 --> 42:08.840
you need to quickly resolve

42:08.840 --> 42:10.320
the previous issues with Mr. Yan.

42:11.440 --> 42:12.680
Don't come for your recent shifts.

42:12.710 --> 42:13.900
Coordinate with others.

42:14.150 --> 42:14.840
If you work night shifts,

42:14.840 --> 42:16.920
and something happens again, it will be hard to explain.

42:17.680 --> 42:19.070
Okay, no problem.

42:40.960 --> 42:48.490
♫So I wait and wander, but the outcome isn't so bad♫

42:48.550 --> 42:55.950
♫Sparrows gather on the windowsill, sunlight streaming through♫

42:48.800 --> 42:49.760
[No homework today?]

42:56.260 --> 43:04.000
♫Poets keep altering words to record the fast-changing world♫

43:04.190 --> 43:11.390
♫A relationship or an accident♫

43:06.160 --> 43:07.200
Is she asleep?

43:08.140 --> 43:10.230
She's been working so hard lately again?
